{"tid":1492134,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"就黎同屋企人割蓆","createTime":"2019-08-20T16:41:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T00:49:12.000Z","uid":201555,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"b214781fd95617ae6900a6ac49db8c38bec48cfd","tid":1492134,"uid":201555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:41:01.000Z","msg":"借acc<br />\n老母一路都唔鍾意我參加集會遊行<br />\n屋企繼7月開始已經無睇過新聞台 老母深紫 連港台都唔想睇<br />\n好啦 咁我咪一路瞞住佢出 瞞住佢貼連儂牆<br />\n點知811去機場俾佢知道咗 佢打電話黎已經癲咗 歇斯底里咁叫我即刻返屋企<br />\n嗰陣一大班人好似出埃及記咁行 行到躁撚到仆街<br />\n嗰晚同跟住第二晚我都去咗朋友屋企住 無返屋企<br />\n因為我係女仔 仲要係第一次無返屋企喺出邊過夜 其實內心已經做好準備割蓆<br />\n不過繼父叫我返下屋企先 所以返咗屋企過咗幾日 相安無事 不過都係無講過嘢<br />\n818我又出咗去 老母啱啱又屌柒我<br />\n將家庭比喻做個社會 話自己點辛苦點辛苦養大我 我反而咁樣對佢<br />\n話政府有咩對我地唔住 話搞事嗰班廢青無份建設香港 上一代養大我地 我地仲搞搞震<br />\n又質疑我點解最近唔洗問屋企攞錢 係咪遊行收錢搞事<br />\n明明只係因為派咗$4000同獎學金 所以先寬裕少少<br />\n<br />\n好多好多廢鳩up不能盡錄 已經無氣屌翻轉頭<br />\n我做好準備搬出黎<br />\n想問巴絲有無邊度地方推薦 又住得落又平嘅地方"},{"pid":"d7e7a61d7f81b21b6665c95087f6d19be849de58","tid":1492134,"uid":2562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:42:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PXcMrux.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPXcMrux.jpg&h=54112853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PN4V4gd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPN4V4gd.jpg&h=bf41982c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/20/233941_35db8952adc66a9b8fad2b475503a348.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F20%2F233941_35db8952adc66a9b8fad2b475503a348.jpeg&h=ba2d15e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0y2D12U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0y2D12U.jpg&h=c7bab806&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pYuV4gf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpYuV4gf.jpg&h=52b2bc94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qMcAke7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqMcAke7.png&h=5d1306ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a21bcf81257ad6ad21fdf0acf83df878e9c1432","tid":1492134,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:43:35.000Z","msg":"元朗啦"},{"pid":"84ef902ee846eaf84254cc5bc90fda7fcf4fcecb","tid":1492134,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:43:52.000Z","msg":"既然你要平"},{"pid":"b73ee435a11c6924970b4dc64cb7d838287357ee","tid":1492134,"uid":22760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:44:03.000Z","msg":"冇錢租唔到樓，劏房都要5000-6000一個月，可以既話照係屋企住住先，劏房環境複雜，個人安全要小心"},{"pid":"62273ddd1457ec9bcf0c5afbf8c890c5c24f6cd4","tid":1492134,"uid":201555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a21bcf81257ad6ad21fdf0acf83df878e9c1432","tid":1492134,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:43:35.000Z","msg":"元朗啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:44:16.000Z","msg":"元朗邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9324f6b058a94e34f181e846a9cbb617efbd232","tid":1492134,"uid":201555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b73ee435a11c6924970b4dc64cb7d838287357ee","tid":1492134,"uid":22760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:44:03.000Z","msg":"冇錢租唔到樓，劏房都要5000-6000一個月，可以既話照係屋企住住先，劏房環境複雜，個人安全要小心"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:45:52.000Z","msg":"我睇緊啲酒店平均二三百一晚"},{"pid":"55df1b6971bfd288daa7d5beeef13f97510da579","tid":1492134,"uid":93253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:47:25.000Z","msg":"邊區"},{"pid":"41fb2e57c2fb93e967f857b479ef7a6f5a04468c","tid":1492134,"uid":22760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9324f6b058a94e34f181e846a9cbb617efbd232","tid":1492134,"uid":201555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b73ee435a11c6924970b4dc64cb7d838287357e